condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Schedule II, Section I, E | Description :No subproject financed without screening by PB, without environmentalanalysis and addressing of env. impacts | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Schedule II, Section I, E | Description :Recipient shall cause the Participating Bank to (i) to implement theProject in accordance with the OM, the EAF and the EMPs (ii) ensure that no subproject has inv. resettlement or land acquis. |Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Schedule II, Section IV, B, 1. | Description :No disbursements for (i) payments made prior to date of signatureof FA or (b) for category 1 unless financial management arrangements satisfactory to IDA have been established for Part A |Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Schedule II, Section V, B. 1 | Description :PBs shall comply with: (a) net loans-to-total deposits below 200%;(b) positive return on assets; (c) non performing loans below 10% of gross loans; (d) non-performing sub loans below 10% |Frequency :Yearly
